io.doov.core.dsl.impl

Class DefaultCondition<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.doov.core.dsl.impl.DefaultCondition<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the field value
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Condition<T>, ContextAccessor<T>, Readable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BooleanCondition, IterableCondition, NumericCondition, StringCondition, TemporalCondition

    public class DefaultCondition<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Base class for all conditions.

    It contains a DslField to get the value from the model, a PredicateMetadata to describe this node, and a BiFunction to take the value from the model and return an optional value.
